## Skills

- `/memory-inspect` — Search and inspect the gemini memory namespace (HNSW + emergent-time decay).
- `/playtest-recap` — Run one full playtest analysis cycle: read → critique balance → model economy → check narrative.

## Commands

- `doctor` — Health-check the gemini: kernel load, MCP wiring, memory backend, host adapter.
- `design-doc-diff` — Diff the current design doc against the previous build and surface unresolved tensions.

## Architecture

This gemini uses [@zagents/kernel](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@zagents/kernel) — a Rust-compiled WASM module with a NAPI-RS native fallback — so the same code runs identically on every platform.
